te curiosity and provide relevant context. Outcomes are the results of actions, not features.\n\n- One of the product model's first principles is innovation over predictability, and another is principles over process.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"59cb1691-6b4c-4678-9974-84f18ed9f1b5","timestamp":"2026-02-08T18:44:16.605Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"8b66b114-d470-495f-adaf-9ab56e2660da"}
